title: opendoor: edit mode support for users
message:
opendoor: edit mode support for users

MainActivity.java: changed name to userActivity (as it handles both edit and add new).
UserActivity.java: edit mode support, get the data from parent activity through intent.
UserListAdapter.java: puts user data on edit button click and calls UserActivity.
activity_user.xml: renamed from activity_new_user.xml
AndroidManifest.xml: renamed NewUserActivity to UserActivity.

title: opendoor: more stable implementation of hang up sleeper
message:
opendoor: more stable implementation of hang up sleeper

Database.java: setSleepTime and getSleepTime methods.
DoorPhone.java: move sleeper into PhoneReceiver, phone number normalization.
IntroActivity.java: new permission (unsure if needed, TODO(willeponken): investigate).
PhoneReceiver.java: receiver for phone call events, looking for CALL_STATE_OFFHOOK event.
SmsReceiver.java: bugfix: moved password declarations into if-clause, caused NULL pointer exception.
User.java: added phone number normalization for constructor.
AndroidManifest.xml: .PhoneReceiver added, added PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALLS permission.
